      },
      {
        "label": "<strong>Charge:&nbsp;</strong><span aria-label=\"cap q sub 1 is equal to 1 half cap q sub 2\"><math> <mrow> <msub> <mi>Q</mi> <mn>1</mn> </msub> <mo>=</mo> <mfrac> <mn>1</mn> <mn>2</mn> </mfrac> <msub> <mi>Q</mi> <mn>2</mn> </msub> </mrow> </math></span><br>\n<br>\n<strong>Potential Difference</strong>: <em>V</em><sub>1</sub> = <em>V</em><sub>2</sub>",
